{"type": "article", "id": 5238, "title": "Gothicism 咖啡机", "description": "", "date": "2015-01-15T07:59:27Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 13, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233526E49KWQrD1LAhHNtY.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;line-height:normal;-webkit-text-stroke-color:#000000;-webkit-text-stroke-width:initial;\">\r\n\t韩国 Dutch Lab 专注于设计高端咖啡器具，推出了以电影、世界建筑与蒸汽朋克等多个主题的咖啡机。这款名为「Gothicism」的咖啡壶属于蒸汽朋克主题中目前价位最高、工艺最复杂的一款，集合了中世纪哥特式建筑高耸入云、繁复华丽的特色，主体采用阳极电镀铝材质，经激光切割，搭配黄铜制造的针阀和硼硅酸盐玻璃管，底部配有一款容量为 150 ml 的烧杯。尽管从性能上来说，Gothicism 与普通冰滴咖啡机并无太大差别，但其复杂的工艺结构已经超越了咖啡机本身，成为一件陈列艺术品。定价 7300 美元（约合人民币 45233 元），<a href=\"http://www.dutch-lab.com/product/gothicism/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;line-height:normal;-webkit-text-stroke-color:#000000;-webkit-text-stroke-width:initial;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233524zxcuD0t2lmOoHFrM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.3625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052335247HnXOv5lZVd6DmJI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233525qa97RtkL2HKi3QuZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233525n9wkVCOQt5yceH4f.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233526DyZLSYrB8Gdma7Iv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}